URL to the kata: https://www.codewars.com/kata/5208f99aee097e6552000148/train/python

Solution:
def solution(s):
    sentence = ""
    word = ""
    for char in s:
        if char.isupper():
            sentence = sentence + word + " "
            word = char
        else:
            word += char
    sentence += word
    return sentence
